12 OCLOCK HIGH 302 Massacre (9/16/1966)

Bombers will bomb Ergen Oil Works, land in Poltava Russia, then hit Berlin on the way back. A straggling Russian Bomber joins the formation and does not give any recognition signals nor does it respond to radio calls. The aircraft is shot down by Major Baladin. Later we learn that the aircraft was piloted by Russian heroes, Major Tobulkan & Captain Chernikov.

Stars: Paul Burke, Frank Overton, Chris Robinson
Guest star: John Zaremba (Lieutenant General Owen), Kevin McCarthy (Baladin), Kathleen Widdoes (Irina Zavanoff), Michael Constantine (Vorodenko), William Wellman, Jr. (Aide)
